title: I get A system Error that randomly restarts my phone
content:
I have been having a restart issue alot I tried talking to google support center but they were not understanding my issue they thought its just software I tried factory resets (all kinds there is). so I started reserching and after opted for Q beta but the phone worked two weeks and back it went into random restart mode. I looked for how I can tell what happens when its going to restart and someone told me about logcat luck enough I start the logging until the phone restarted itself and it stoped and its last messages should be able to tell what is happening but I can't understand them. I need some help with interpreting them and recomendations for a solution.
